# Source code rules (when implemented)

- Organise by journey and `integration/` Gen client — not by duplicate entity DB.
- Map Gen DTOs in `integration/`; UI labels in `mobile/` only.
- Read `architecture/mvp/solution-overview.md` before new modules.
- Tests in `tests/integration/` for OpenAPI contracts; avoid mock-only truth for Gen behaviour.
